{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id909e7b09-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s5856"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5856"},"text":"§ 5856.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Soviet weapons destruction","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id909e7b0a-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s5856/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":", (b) Omitted","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id909e7b0b-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6","identifier":"/us/usc/t22/s5856/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Avoidance of duplicative amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The amendments made by this section shall not be effective if the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 1993 enacts an amendment to section 221(a) of the Soviet Nuclear Threat Reduction Act of 1991 that authorizes the transfer of an amount that is the same or greater than the amount that is authorized by the amendment made by subsection (a)(1) of this section and enacts amendments identical to those in subsections (a)(2) and (b) of this section. If that Act enacts such amendments, sections 5853 and 5858 of this title shall be deemed to apply with respect to the funds made available under such amendments.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id909e7b0c-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/511/tV/s506"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–511, title V, § 506","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-24"},"text":"Oct. 24, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/3341"},"text":"106 Stat. 3341","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id909e7b0d-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id909e7b0e-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id909e7b0f-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For the amendments made by this section, referred to in subsec. (c), see Codification note below.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 1993, referred to in subsec. (c), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/484"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–484","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-23"},"text":"Oct. 23, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/2315"},"text":"106 Stat. 2315","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Tables. See, also, Codification note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 221(a) of the Soviet Nuclear Threat Reduction Act of 1991, referred to in subsec. (c), was ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/228/s221/a"},"text":"section 221(a) of Pub. L. 102–228","children":[],"tail":", which was set out in a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2551"},"text":"section 2551 of this title","children":[],"tail":" prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/291/dA/tXIII/s1351/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–291, div. A, title XIII, § 1351(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/3606"},"text":"128 Stat. 3606","children":[],"tail":". See Codification note below."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id909e7b10-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/511/s506"},"text":"section 506 of Pub. L. 102–511","children":[],"tail":". Subsec. (a) of this section directed the amendment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/228/s221"},"text":"section 221 of Pub. L. 102–228","children":[],"tail":", which was set out in a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2551"},"text":"section 2551 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/291/dA/tXIII/s1351/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–291, div. A, title XIII, § 1351(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/3606"},"text":"128 Stat. 3606","children":[],"tail":". Subsec. (b) of this section directed the amendment of sections 108 and 109 of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/229"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–229","children":[],"tail":", which are not classified to the Code. Because of amendments by section 1421(a)(2)(B), (3) and (b) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/484/dA/tXIV"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–484, div. A, title XIV","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-23"},"text":"Oct. 23, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/2565"},"text":"106 Stat. 2565","children":[],"tail":", to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/228/s221"},"text":"section 221 of Pub. L. 102–228","children":[],"tail":" and sections 108 and 109 of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/229"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–229","children":[],"tail":", the amendments directed by subsecs. (a) and (b) of this section did not take effect pursuant to subsec. (c) of this section."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
